      <p>Electrical faults are responsible for a significant portion of house fires in Pakistan every year. Ageing wiring, overloaded circuits, and do-it-yourself electrical work done without proper knowledge are the main culprits. Yet most homeowners pay little attention to their electrical system until something goes wrong — by which point, it may be too late to prevent serious injury, fire, or costly property damage.</p>

