      <p>Water-based emulsion paints are the most popular interior choice in Pakistan for good reason: they dry quickly, have low odour, are easy to clean up, and are available in a vast colour range. For living rooms and bedrooms, a good quality emulsion from brands like Berger, ICI Dulux, Nippon, or Master Paints will serve well.</p>
